text: Bluebird is the fourth studio album by American musician Dawn Landes. It was released on February 18, 2014 on Western Vinyl. ==Critical reception== Bluebird was met with generally favorable reviews from critics. At Metacritic, which assigns a weighted average rating out of 100 to reviews from mainstream publications, this release received an average score of 75, based on 7 reviews. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2014 albums Category:Western Vinyl albums
